{"tid":1200140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我都覺得和理非冇用但","createTime":"2019-06-10T16:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T16:45:13.000Z","uid":88813,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a1044c1f33ef14cee980f4d9c59a6a79f02f4f04","tid":1200140,"uid":88813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"望住一個個討論噚晚衝突<br />\n講和理非真係唔會有用<br />\n我知呀, 我明呀, 我曾經同你講一模一樣嘅說話<br />\n我到今日都仲係咁諗<br />\n但對唔住我真係實踐唔到勇武 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你決定離開和理非嘅道路<br />\n喺你面前就只有無窮無盡嘅暴力<br />\n<br />\n掟垃圾桶同掟汽油彈唔會有分別<br />\n個社會一樣會鬧你<br />\n個法庭一樣會重判你<br />\n<br />\n所以你如果決定唔再和理非<br />\n就應該將你有辦法得到嘅最高級嘅暴力拎曬出嚟<br />\n電鋸又好, 汽油彈又好, 土製菠蘿又好<br />\n甚至你有本事搵到槍的話都應該拎定出嚟<br />\n除咗武器之外<br />\n你仲應該每日操練體能<br />\n每日排練對抗嘅陣式<br />\n直到你嘅暴力終於戰勝警察<br />\n<br />\n唔係我想鼓吹暴力<br />\n而係邏輯上你只要離開和理非就必然會得到以上結論<br />\n<br />\n但有幾可行?<br />\n你得, 你身邊嘅同伴又得唔得?<br />\n叫你買把牛肉刀買碌鐵通去同警察死過你敢唔敢?<br />\n反正衰咗一樣要坐, 點解唔去盡啲?<br />\n因為淆呀, 我都淆<br />\n所以我話我實踐唔到<br />\n<br />\n警察真係收咗錢日操夜操<br />\n仲有無限金錢買裝備, 點鬥?<br />\n<br />\n過咗咁耐<br />\n我真係唔識判斷和理非同武勇<br />\n邊一樣會比較容易挑戰港共政權<br />\n定其實點都係死路一條 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位迷惘嘅巴絲<br />\n我迷惘咗差唔多五年喇<br />\n原諒我到今日都未畀到答案出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1155effe71b0a600b87da872690e74b1b37ead7d","tid":1200140,"uid":34515,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:33:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">迷惘唔緊要 唔同角色有唔同崗位可以幫手 你怕暴力 就做後援 記住今次得一個目標</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/11/003257_509aab227c0e7eee27f2ed358cf41cec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F11%2F003257_509aab227c0e7eee27f2ed358cf41cec.png&h=29d0e1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（文宣組）612icon<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199744</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n【大整合】11/6-12/6 資訊整合 「反送中」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199978</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n〔置頂〕唔通溫和派就無嘢可以做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199622</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港加油 各有各做！</span></span>"},{"pid":"20f49882fc4cddae0217d7dce634d2503d531ede","tid":1200140,"uid":88813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1155effe71b0a600b87da872690e74b1b37ead7d","tid":1200140,"uid":34515,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:33:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">迷惘唔緊要 唔同角色有唔同崗位可以幫手 你怕暴力 就做後援 記住今次得一個目標</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/11/003257_509aab227c0e7eee27f2ed358cf41cec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F11%2F003257_509aab227c0e7eee27f2ed358cf41cec.png&h=29d0e1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（文宣組）612icon<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199744</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n【大整合】11/6-12/6 資訊整合 「反送中」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199978</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n〔置頂〕唔通溫和派就無嘢可以做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199622</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港加油 各有各做！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:45:13.000Z","msg":"盡做，但我依家真係冒唔起風險"}]}